      "options": [],
      "sourcePage": 4,
      "sourceMode": "text",
      "ocrUsed": false,
      "answer": "Module 9 (June 2022 Session) Page 7 of 7 * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * * Answer 6(b) The conveyance on sale (\"COS\") Ad valorem stamp duty (\"AVD\") The COS dated 31 October 2019 is executed not in conformity with the earlier ASP because Simon's spouse Judy owned another residential property in Hong Kong on 31 October 2019. As the nominee Judy is a close relative of the purchaser Simon, the COS is ch argeable with AVD at the scale 2 rates based on the half share interest assigned by Simon to Judy by reference to the value of the Property at the date of conveyance. The amount of AVD is as follows: AVD = HK$9,000,000 x 3.75% x ½ = HK$168,750 Special stamp duty (\"SSD\") Simon assigned half share of the Property to his spouse Judy within 36 months after acquisition on 1 September 2019 but is exempt from SSD because the nominee Judy is the purchaser's close relative. Buyer's stamp duty (\"BSD\") The COS is not chargeable with BSD as the nominee Judy is a close relative of the purchaser.\nThe conveyance on sale (\"COS\")\nAd valorem stamp duty (\"AVD\")\nThe COS dated 31 October 2019 is executed not in conformity with the earlier ASP because\nSimon's spouse Judy owned another residential property in Hong Kong on 31 October 2019.\nAs the nominee Judy is a close relative of the purchaser Simon, the COS is chargeable with\nAVD at the scale 2 rates based on the half share interest assigned by Simon to Judy by\nreference to the value of the Property at the date of conveyance. The amount of AVD is as\nfollows:\nAVD = HK$9,000,000 x 3.75% x > = HK$168,750\nSpecial stamp duty (\"SSD\")\nSimon assigned half share of the Property to his spouse Judy within 36 months after\nacquisition on 1 September 2019 but is exempt from SSD because the nominee Judy is the\npurchaser's close relative.\nBuyer's stamp duty (\"BSD\")\nThe COS is not chargeable with BSD as the nominee Judy is a close relative of the\npurchaser.\n* * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *\nModule 9 (June 2022 Session) Page 7 of 7\nCPA hid pibiic Accountants\n-_ SERNGLR",
