      "answer": "Module 7 (June 2022 Session) Page 6 of 6 Answer 4(d) Sustainable growth rate should be higher than the internal growth rate because: - By comparing the formulas for sustainable growth rate and internal growth rate, ROE is larger than ROA. - For the sustainable growth rate, Little Ox will have to borrow additional debt to maintain a constant debt to equity ratio. The total assets will be increased by this extra debt financing in addition to the internally generated fund from retained earn ings. As such, Little Ox can expand more rapidly than the internal growth rate. * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *",
