      "answer": "Module 6 (June 2024 Session) Page 13 of 13 Answer 4(b) In accordance with HKFRS 16, at the commencement date, a lessor recognises assets held under a finance lease in its statement of financial position and presents them as a receivable at an amount equal to the net investment in the lease. Gross investment in the lease at the commencement date = HK$1,170,068 (HK$198,000 x 5 + HK$180,068). Net investment in the lease at the commencement date = HK$900,000, calculated as follows: Date Nature Amount Discounted amount 30 Sept 2023 1 st rental payment HK$198,000   (1 + 8.5%) = HK$182,488 30 Sept 2024 2 nd rental payment HK$198,000   (1 + 8.5%) 2 = HK$168,192 30 Sept 2025 3 rd rental payment HK$198,000   (1 + 8.5%) 3 = HK$155,016 30 Sept 2026 4 th rental payment HK$198,000   (1 + 8.5%) 4 = HK$142,871 30 Sept 2027 5 th rental payment HK$198,000   (1 + 8.5%) 5 = HK$131,679 Unguarantee d residual value HK$180,068   (1 + 8.5%) 5 = HK$119,753 Total HK$900,000 (rounded) Total finance income over the 5 years = HK$270,068 (HK$1,170,068 – HK$900,000). * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *\nIn accordance with HKFRS 16, at the commencement date, a lessor recognises assets held\nunder a finance lease in its statement of financial position and presents them as a receivable\nat an amount equal to the net investment in the lease.\nGross investment in the lease at the commencement date = HK$1,170,068 (HK$198,000 x\n5 + HK$180,068).\nNet investment in the lease at the commencement date = HK$900,000, calculated as follows:\nDate Nature Amount Discounted\namount\n30 Sept 2023 1%! rental HK$198,000 / (1+ 8.5%) = HK$182,488\npayment\n30 Sept 2024 2\" rental HK$198,000 / (1+ 8.5%)? = HK$168,192\npayment\n30 Sept 2025 3\" rental HK$198,000 / (1+8.5%)° = HK$155,016\npayment\n30 Sept 2026 4\" rental HK$198,000 / (1+ 8.5%)\" = HK$142,871\npayment\n30 Sept 2027 5\" rental HK$198,000 / (1+8.5%)° = HK$131,679\npayment\nUnguarantee HK$180,068 / (1+ 8.5%)° = HK$119,753\nd residual\nvalue\nTotal HK$900,000\n(rounded)\nTotal finance income over the 5 years = HK$270,068 (HK$1,170,068 — HK$900,000).\n* * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *\nModule 6 (June 2024 Session) Page 13 of 13\nCPA hid rabiic Accountants\n-~_ FReHFLE",
