      "prompt": "Module 5 (December 2022 Session) Page 4 of 4 Question 4 (18 marks – approximately 32 minutes) (a) List any TWO types of information needs per each of the following function areas: (i) human resources; and (2 marks) (ii) marketing. (2 marks) (b) Although cloud computing is becoming popular nowadays, many organisations are still running their information systems with a client-server model on their premises . Required: (i) Contrast any THREE differences between a server and a client. (6 marks) (ii) Justify the importance of using a network switch in a client-server network. You should start by describing the functions of a network switch. (3 marks) Question 5 (13 marks – approximately 24 minutes) (a) Determine any TWO risks that may occur if an e-commerce business has weak identity authentication among its customers and suppliers. (4 marks) (b) Contrast the differences between e-commerce and e-business. (5 marks) (c) According to a global survey conducted by an international CPA firm in 2021, 78% of respondents are currently implementing Robotic Process Automation (RPA) and 16% of respondents plan to do so in the next three years. Required: (i) Define \"Robotic Process Automation\" (RPA). (2 marks) (ii) List any TWO examples of using RPA in accounting. (2 marks) * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *",
      "full": "Module 5 (December 2022 Session) Page 4 of 4 Question 4 (18 marks – approximately 32 minutes) (a) List any TWO types of information needs per each of the following function areas: (i) human resources; and (2 marks) (ii) marketing. (2 marks) (b) Although cloud computing is becoming popular nowadays, many organisations are still running their information systems with a client-server model on their premises . Required: (i) Contrast any THREE differences between a server and a client. (6 marks) (ii) Justify the importance of using a network switch in a client-server network. You should start by describing the functions of a network switch. (3 marks) Question 5 (13 marks – approximately 24 minutes) (a) Determine any TWO risks that may occur if an e-commerce business has weak identity authentication among its customers and suppliers. (4 marks) (b) Contrast the differences between e-commerce and e-business. (5 marks) (c) According to a global survey conducted by an international CPA firm in 2021, 78% of respondents are currently implementing Robotic Process Automation (RPA) and 16% of respondents plan to do so in the next three years. Required: (i) Define \"Robotic Process Automation\" (RPA). (2 marks) (ii) List any TWO examples of using RPA in accounting. (2 marks) * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *",
      "options": [],
      "sourcePage": 4,
      "sourceMode": "text",
      "ocrUsed": false,
      "answer": "Module 5 (December 2022 Session) Page 7 of 7 - preparing a bank reconciliation by matching transactions between a bank statement and a bank ledger account; - automating pre- and/or post- payment validation; or - monitoring and identifying potential duplicate payments, * * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *\n- preparing a bank reconciliation by matching transactions between a bank statement and\na bank ledger account;\n- automating pre- and/or post- payment validation; or\n- monitoring and identifying potential duplicate payments,\n* * * END OF EXAMINATION PAPER * * *\nModule 5 (December 2022 Session) Page 7 of 7\nCPA ciied pibiic Accountants\n-~_ FReHFLE",
